&                                                            ;TRICCE4 Desc;TRICCE5 Desc;TRICCE6 Desc
  When  5 : Filter [TMP] Where NUMREQ=REQUETE Order By Key CLE=TRICCE1 Desc;TRICCE2 Desc;TRICCE3 Desc
&                                                            ;TRICCE4 Desc;TRICCE5 Desc
